    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> why did you hit Ctrl-Space?\n\nLike pgcli binding overwrite suggests :) \nIn some modern editors <kbd>Ctrl+Space</kbd> invokes completion, and I guess I pressed that instead <kbd>Tab</kbd> in a \"semi-automated/semi-conscious\" state.\n\n> Maybe there should be an 'emacs-lite' editing mode which disables some of these less familiar emacs features?\n\nThat would be nice if easily possible, for users not familiar with vi or emacs\n"
